l":"News Digest","trigger":"schedule","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-10T22:00:00.011Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-11T06:03:37.580Z","status":"error","summary":null,"error":"Failed after 3 attempts. Last error: Cannot connect to API: ","itemCount":null},{"id":"1eeb9f65-bf37-4e1c-a6a6-4fbd23bcf4af","job":"convertprivately-article","label":"ConvertPrivately Article","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-09T09:16:54.372Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-09T09:20:36.520Z","status":"success","summary":"ConvertPrivately article published: OpenAI Audio Models & Anthropic’s ‘Dreaming’ Feature Change the AI Privacy Surface\nhttps://convertprivately.com/insights/openai-audio-models-anthropic-dreaming-privacy-surface\n\nSource queue item: OpenAI Audio Models & Anthropic''s ''Dreaming'' Feature Among Latest AI Updates","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"8e08bf85-504f-4e4f-aa30-71e69eece179","job":"personal-research","label":"Personal Research","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-06T21:28:55.331Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-06T21:30:30.584Z","status":"success","summary":"Personal research: created note \"PDF redaction failures — technical deep dive: black box over text, metadata residue, incremental saves, glyph positioning, link/bookmark leaks, The Epstein files redaction disaster (Dec 2025 – Feb 2026) — technical post-mortem: what was exposed, how, why, \"Files deleted after 2 hours\" is not enough — privacy policy analysis of the top 10 online file converters (Smallpdf, iLovePDF, Convertio, FreeConvert, Zamzar, PDF24, CloudConvert, Adobe Online, Soda PDF, Sejda), Q1 2026 data breaches involving files and documents — roundup with focus on third-party file processing as attack vector (LexisNexis, UH Cancer Center, LAPD, Companies House UK, France Titres), How many public PDFs still hide redacted data? — original benchmark study replicating the University of Wisconsin methodology (\"Story Beyond the Eye: Glyph Positions Break PDF Text Redaction\") on a public dataset (FOIA releases, CourtListener) using the x-ray library — 2026-05-06\" with 1 sources.\nSaved to data/research/2026-05-06T21-30-30-212Z-pdf-redaction-failures-technical-deep-dive-black-box-over-te.md","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"a5b3b7f7-683a-461e-be94-6048f5193931","job":"convertprivately-article","label":"ConvertPrivately Article","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-06T21:11:21.990Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-06T21:16:07.051Z","status":"success","summary":"ConvertPrivately article published: Shields Up: Defending Local File Workflows Against AI-Enabled Attacks\nhttps://convertprivately.com/insights/cisco-shields-up-ai-attacks-local-workflows\n\nSource queue item: Cisco Issues Guidance on Defending Against AI-Enabled Cyber Attacks","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"137257bf-0afd-4a61-aee9-3c9b2a540d20","job":"news-digest","label":"News Digest","trigger":"schedule","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T18:00:00.052Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T18:01:57.212Z","status":"success","summary":"News digest: +2 in coda (13 scartati, 2 già visti, 38 in attesa di pubblicazione)\n\n• Microsoft and Sony Adjust Console Release Strategies Amid Survey Data\n  A new consumer survey indicates console players still value exclusive games, though that driver has declined year-over-year. Both Sony and Xbox are adjusting their multi-platform release strategies accordingly.\n  motivo: Industry analysis on shifting console exclusivity strategies for Xbox and PlayStation, backed by Circana consumer survey data.\n  https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/technology/gaming/microsoft-and-sonys-evolving-game-release-strategy-may-be-aligned-with-console-players-survey-suggests/articleshow/130733423.cms\n\n• Rural New Mexico Hospital Integrates Ambient AI for Clinical Documentation\n  A rural hospital in New Mexico has integrated ambient AI directly into its electronic health record system to assist doctors with clinical note-taking and documentation workflows.\n  motivo: Real-world AI adoption story detailing ambient AI integration into electronic health records for clinical documentation.\n  https://www.santafenewmexican.com/news/health_and_science/at-one-rural-new-mexico-hospital-doctors-turn-to-ai-tools/article_3b4bb6d6-dccf-41c8-9da4-72fce954060d.html","error":null,"itemCount":2},{"id":"47f1aa94-9356-4cce-81b7-ed3ca91b0af7","job":"tweet-post","label":"Tweet Post","trigger":"schedule","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T17:30:00.039Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T17:31:14.586Z","status":"success","summary":"Tweet pubblicato (witty):\nAI isn’t just editing articles anymore—it’s writing them. Media leaders at Hampton University are debating if artificial intelligence is a newsroom upgrade or a trust killer. Press freedom goes algorithmic. — ConvertPrivately.com\n\nLink: https://x.com/Calogero1975/status/2050991583865024981","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"cd9724a4-828b-42d2-9f0b-a4bffd401451","job":"tweet-post","label":"Tweet Post","trigger":"schedule","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T12:30:00.006Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T12:30:59.750Z","status":"success","summary":"Tweet pubblicato (witty):\nAI isn’t just running on GPUs anymore. It’s running on hard hats and union labor. Tech giants are finally partnering with building trades to construct the data centers that will power tomorrow’s models. The blue-collar boom is here. — ConvertPrivately.com\n\nLink: https://x.com/Calogero1975/status/2050916023948157111","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"23a1b691-779b-4492-a694-cf96c9bcde9b","job":"news-digest","label":"News Digest","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T08:35:11.476Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T08:37:23.835Z","status":"success","summary":"News digest: +2 in coda (16 scartati, 1 già visti, 48 in attesa di pubblicazione)\n\n• IISER Tirupati Opens AI & Data Science Master''s Admissions\n  The institute offers online one-year professional master’s tracks in Biological Data Science and DS-AI for 2026-2027 admissions.\n  motivo: Admissions open for one-year professional master’s programmes in Data Science and AI at IISER Tirupati, targeting working professionals with applied learning pathways.\n  https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/education/news/iiser-tirupati-opens-admissions-for-one-year-biods-and-ds-ai-professional-masters-programmes-for-2026/articleshow/130728210.cms\n\n• Sakana AI Introduces KAME Real-Time LLM Injection Architecture\n  The hybrid architecture bridges fast direct S2S response times with deep reasoning capabilities by conditioning audio output on streaming LLM oracles.\n  motivo: Sakana AI unveils KAME, a tandem speech-to-speech model that maintains near-zero latency while injecting real-time LLM knowledge via oracle streams.\n  https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/05/03/sakana-ai-introduces-kame-a-tandem-speech-to-speech-architecture-that-injects-llm-knowledge-in-real-time/","error":null,"itemCount":2},{"id":"77674230-498e-412a-8a36-050247075599","job":"tweet-post","label":"Tweet Post","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T08:31:30.292Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T08:33:54.704Z","status":"success","summary":"Tweet pubblicato (factual):\nGenAI is hitting production, making prompt injection and data leakage risks. A new architecture pairs Enkrypt’s governance platform with Citrix NetScaler to lock down enterprise apps. Secure deployment isn’t optional anymore—it’s the baseline. — ConvertPrivately.com\n\nLink: https://x.com/Calogero1975/status/2050856360045068302","error":null,"itemCount":1},{"id":"878ae4f3-96ed-43ce-8eb5-a0b98fa23870","job":"tweet-post","label":"Tweet Post","trigger":"manual","modelAlias":"qwen","startedAt":"2026-05-03T08:28:45.291Z","finishedAt":"2026-05-03T08:28:59.573Z","status":"success","summary":"Tweet job: nessun articolo pubblicabile (46 in coda, nessuno nella finestra 24h).","error":null,"itemCount":0},{"id":"6db9a850-0c7f-4977-8732-fd49c0e9a852","job":"tweet-po