INSERT OR IGNORE INTO 'app_kv'(_rowid_, 'key', 'value_json', 'updated_at') VALUES (14, 'assistant.conversations', '{"version":1,"conversations":{"166518390721109":[{"role":"user","content":"Could you run the news worker?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nThe news worker has returned its report. Here are the top headlines from today:\n\n*   **Global Protests:** \"''No Kings'' rallies draw crowds across U.S. and Europe,\" featuring a notable demonstration in Minnesota headlined by Springsteen.\n*   **General Coverage:** Major outlets like The Hindu, Times of India, and ABC News are currently pushing breaking national and world news updates.\n\nWould you like me to fetch the full text for any specific story?"},{"role":"user","content":"yes, the 1st one"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nHere are the details on the ''No Kings'' rally:\n\n**Event Overview**\nOn Saturday, March 28, 2026, massive crowds gathered across the U.S. and Europe for \"No Kings\" rallies. The Minnesota demonstration at the State Capitol in St. Paul was designated as the national flagship event.\n\n**Key Highlights**\n*   **Bruce Springsteen:** The iconic musician headlined the Minnesota rally, performing songs including one introduced as \"Streets of Minneapolis.\"\n*   **Purpose:** The protests were organized against the war in Iran and President Trump''s aggressive immigration policies.\n*   **Atmosphere:** Thousands attended, described as standing shoulder-to-shoulder to celebrate resistance.\n\nThe PBS report notes that while rallies occurred globally, Minnesota took center stage for this specific demonstration."},{"role":"user","content":"Hi, what''s up?"},{"role":"user","content":"Hi, what''s up?"},{"role":"user","content":"Hi, what''s up?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nHello again. Everything is running smoothly here. How can I help you today?"},{"role":"user","content":"hi"},{"role":"user","content":"hi"},{"role":"user","content":"hi"},{"role":"user","content":"Hey! What''s up?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nHey. All systems operational and ready to go. What’s on your mind?"},{"role":"user","content":"I''m just doing some test, as the application is almost ready to be published"},{"role":"user","content":"oops, what happened?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nAll systems nominal on my end. Did you encounter a specific error during your test run, or was that just a transmission hiccup? Let me know what needs fixing."},{"role":"user","content":"ok, it have been just a random hiccup"},{"role":"assistant","content":"\n\nUnderstood. Glad we''re back on track. Let me know if you need anything else before launch."},{"role":"user","content":"what''s up?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"All systems nominal. Standing by. What do you need?"},{"role":"user","content":"What are the latest news fetched?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"I don’t have a fresh news fetch in this chat right now.\n\nIf you want, I can:\n- run the news worker again, or\n- search for specific topics you care about.\n\nGive me a topic, and I’ll pull the latest."},{"role":"user","content":"what''s the latest news?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"I’ve kicked off the news worker. It’ll return a fresh digest shortly.\n\nIf you want, I can tailor the next pass to:\n- world news\n- tech\n- business\n- a specific country or topic"},{"role":"user","content":"tech"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Done. I’ve queued a tech-focused news digest.\n\nIf you want, I can also narrow it further:\n- AI\n- Apple / Google / Microsoft\n- cybersecurity\n- startups\n- semiconductors"},{"role":"user","content":"What are the latest news in the bus?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Latest items in the bus, newest first:\n\n- **PayPal news: banking push and UPI-linked payments developments** — queued, 2m ago  \n- **Kyndryl Cloud Uplift expands into Japan** — queued, 2m ago  \n- **Fraunhofer Launches CICERO Project for AI-Driven Hospital Cobots** — queued, 5h ago  \n- **Europe''s Largest AI Event,